Package: gmmDenoise
Version: 0.2.1
Title: A set of functions for GMM-based denoising of metabarcoding sequence data
Authors@R: person(given = "Yusuke",
                  family = "Koseki",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "ykoseki@otsuma.ac.jp",
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9588-3018"))
Description: A set of functions for denoising amplicon sequence variants (ASVs)
    in metabarcoding analysis, based on Gaussian mixture modeling (GMM).
